pr_body:
**This PR resolves #5**

I have worked on the following feature:
- Complete the data extraction feature (skills and the interests of the user).
- Create two python **sets** (skills and interests) containing lots of data points (like programming languages and tech-related fields)
- Make a function **processMessageL1()** to iterate over the sets and find the data points in the message
- Store the matched keywords (data points) in the respective array variables

**Image showing the sets containing the data points**
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/55585868/123084022-51c72a80-d43e-11eb-9f8f-9386ee283d00.png)
